title: Gossip | Watch: The only thing better than Selena Gomez's Dubsmashes is watching her make Dubsmashes
text:
We all know that Selena Gomez can lip sync so it stands to reason that her Dubsmashing skills would be on point and thankfully they are.
Gomez appeared on The Tonight Show with Jimmy Fallon last night to promote her new album and tour and Fallon being Fallon he pulled out an iPad and the two played a game of Dubsmash, with Gomez putting Fallon to shame in their Dubsmash off.
She also showed off her 'ghost app' that she uses to find ghosts around her because she believes in them so much.
We'd concentrate on the lip syncing more if we were her. She'll need it for that tour.
Via YouTube
